title: TB1 - I'M BLESSED
seo_description:
the multiple award-winning TB1 (The Blessed One) Leader Of The BLW Rap Nation, arguably one of the best Gospel rappers in Africa, popularly known for his unique rapping and writing skills, has the jaws of millions of his fans drop with the release of a "No Rap" dancing Jam produced by MayoMuziq titled I'M BLESSED

The song, which is a celebration jam already, has lovers of TB1 music on their feet dancing.
